1061-商業時事分析課程公告(全英語授課)
教師：駱世民老師
課程時段：3hi
課號：125151
為了打造良好的上課品質，讓同學們於個案討論時可以充分發揮，1061本課程人數上限30人。
故請想修課的同學，請於6/30前，填妥個人資料表如附檔（組員資料表留空）與一頁修課動機，請皆以英文撰寫，將文件寄到助教信箱（Email住址會使用灌水程式保護機制。你需要啟動Javascript才能觀看它 ）即可。
如果還有任何疑問，請聯絡助教楊子嬉。

Course title : Business News and Analysis
Instructor : Professor Lo
Course Number: 125151
In order to create a great learning environment for the course and have a fully case discussion for every student, 30 students at maximum are allowed to be enrolled. 
For those who are interested in this course, please fill out the attached Personal Information Form while leaving the bottom part of it to be empty and write a one-page writeup about your statement of purpose. Please submit it by email to TA,Cece Yang (Email住址會使用灌水程式保護機制。你需要啟動Javascript才能觀看它).
The deadline of submission: June 30
If you have any further question, please contact TA, Cece Yang 


